The paper proposes a design for a CNN accelerator, which is a topic related to computer architecture (cs.AR) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the difficulty of programming FPGAs, which falls under the category of electronic design automation (cs.ET). The proposed design also involves scheduling and tiling of neural network layers, which is related to control systems (cs.SY) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
